    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/14/125391187/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_5913733993535411508.png",
                "key": "我流劍術",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "我流劍術"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">亂嵐撥止</span>。</p><p>如果此技能引發了擴散，則將<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">亂嵐撥止</span>轉換為被擴散的元素。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此技能結算後：</span>我方切換到後一個角色。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">亂嵐撥止</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色進行下落攻擊時：</span>造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>變為<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，且傷害+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">角色使用技能後：</span>移除此效果。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/14/125391187/33d0a2ad4ba893402e879d35ab6ce233_3628069050618152462.png",
                "key": "千早振",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "千早振"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">流風秋野</span>。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/14/125391187/3b2e6b2c4ffbc7d13d7f2461cb4497e9_5286071609632533445.png",
                "key": "萬葉之一刀",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "萬葉之一刀"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：3</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色或召喚物引發擴散反應後：</span>轉換此牌的元素類型，改為造成被擴散的元素類型的傷害。(離場前僅限一次)</p>",
                "icon_url": "",
                "key": "流風秋野",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/14/125391187/692a68ca67cd7fa11e0c225fb1540804_4895937232014745313.png",
                "title": "流風秋野"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（冰）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（水）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（火）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（雷）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/14/125391187/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_8248940170395277525.png",
                "key": "風元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "風元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">下落攻擊</span></strong></p><p>角色被切換為「出戰角色」後，本回合內的下一個戰鬥行為若為「普通攻擊」，則被視為「下落攻擊」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/14/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_2806739200224999885.png",
                "key": "規則解釋",
